description:
This is a 6 minute workout called '50 Different Exercises using the Airdyne Bike - Full Body Workout' from the channel George Doumanian Jr.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
